<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.10.2">
<l>kontalarnta naṟuntuḻāy cāntan tūpan tīpaṅkoṇṭa marartoḻap paṇaṅkoḷ pāmpil</l>
<l>cantaṇimeṉ mulaimalarāḷ taraṇi maṅkai tāmiruva raṭivaruṭun taṉmai yāṉai</l>
<l>vantaṉaicey ticaiyēḻā ṟaṅka maintu vaḷarvēḷvi nāṉmaṟaikaḷ mūṉṟu tīyum</l>
<l>cintaṉaicey tirupoḻutu moṉṟum celvat tirukkōva lūrataṉuḷ kaṇṭēṉ nāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having done homage to the one whose appearance on a serpent with hoods</l>
<l rend="indent">is with both lady earth and the lotus lady,</l>
<l rend="indent">with sandalwood adorned soft breasts, stroking his feet,</l>
<l>While celestials worship, [bearing] clusters of fragrant, blooming tulasī,</l>
<l rend="indent">sandalwood, incense, and lamps,</l>
<l>I saw [him] in prosperous Tirukkōvalūr where, with seven modes of music,</l>
<l rend="indent">the six branches of knowledge,</l>
<l>Five nurtured rites, the four Vedas, and three fires,</l>
<l rend="indent">performing meditation two times daily, it is at one [with him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
